// | CTRL  | EXTRA | TABP | TABN | UBER | NUMB | /**/ | INS   | -     | =    | [  | ]     | \    |
// | SHIFT | PLAY  | PREV | NEXT | VDN  | VUP  | /**/ | PRINT | LEFT  | DOWN | UP | RIGHT | DEL  |
//                        | LALT | HELD | SPC  | /**/ | ENTER | RAISE | GUI  |

bindings = <
    &kp GRAVE  &kp N1            &kp N2      &kp N3      &kp N4        &kp N5       /**/ &kp N6     &kp N7     &kp N8     &kp N9    &kp N0     &kp BSPC
    &kp LCTRL  &mo EXTRA         &tab_prev   &tab_next   &mo UBER      &mo NUMBER   /**/ &kp INS    &kp MINUS  &kp EQUAL  &kp LBKT  &kp RBKT   &kp BSLH
